	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />How many nametable tiles are you pushing out per frame during the Nyan-cat sequence?
<br />
<br />In my Chu Chu Rocket game, I was pushing out 216 tiles per frame in NTSC mode, and had to turn the screen on 3 scanlines into the frame.  But PAL mode has a much longer vblank time and you can push out far more tiles.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


